abstract: College Basketball Roundup; Monmouth University defeats University of Notre Dame 70-68; other basketball news and scores noted.
lead_paragraph: Monmouth upset No. 17 Notre Dame, 70-68, on Thursday night in the first round of the AdvoCare Invitational in Lake Buena Vista, Fla.

headline.main: Monmouth Cuts Down Another Big Opponent: Notre Dame
headline.print_headline: Monmouth Knocks Off Notre Dame in Thriller
